{"tid":1303344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【同台灣政府協商】建一個港人聚居地　有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-07-10T09:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T10:43:57.000Z","uid":14328,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"62a9e1921f389428878de31afaad5a3b9e145eca","tid":1303344,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:39:59.000Z","msg":"留意到有人想集資去買島買船建地，但呢個方案我感覺好似發展星際移民咁遠。做生不如做熟，同台灣政府協商，建一個港人聚居地？呢個方案可以話係對香港好，對台灣綠營政府更好既方案。<br />\n<br />\n一）台灣綠營政府一直被中共打壓，與港人立場相似<br />\n<br />\n二）港人移民過去之後，將成為台灣綠營嘅新票倉<br />\n<br />\n三）如果可以低價低門檻移民去台灣，唔少香港人願意去台中台南呢啲人口老化地區<br />\n<br />\n四）港人移民過去，將帶來台灣大量新資金。<br />\n<br />\n五）撥一個新市鎮比香港人重點聚居兼做開荒牛，以香港人團結程度，假以時日，果度將會係一個「新香港」，別具特色風味，將來可以成為新旅遊區。<br />\n<br />\n六）香港移民大多位年輕人，有氣有力既勞動人口／高智商高學歷既才幹，以舒緩台灣地區人口老化、經濟發展緩慢既問題。<br />\n<br />\n七）軍事上，某些港人反共意志比台灣鷹派更高，參軍嘅話，可以即時同融入台灣軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n對綠營既好處真係多到數唔哂，對藍營／台灣入面嘅共狗，只有不利。小英真係可以認真考慮。"},{"pid":"eeb2681ce677ccb169acece6d6c57aa6b133b4ff","tid":1303344,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:41:20.000Z","msg":"ＰＵＳＨ"},{"pid":"375f9d69bc4f12c98a75a2f56c13903ac4a934ee","tid":1303344,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b85e8386c95e243eff709480ad01ecb3acbd338","tid":1303344,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"但係你可能要諗再走過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬一有年俾發大財贏到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df09e54036a49636aea6dbc6e925798ed7771dd","tid":1303344,"uid":14328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b85e8386c95e243eff709480ad01ecb3acbd338","tid":1303344,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"但係你可能要諗再走過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬一有年俾發大財贏到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"過左去既香港人將會極力阻止呢樣野發生<br />\n<br />\n如果台灣人投票比發大財嘅唯一原因只係經濟<br />\n<br />\n我地過到去亦可以死命谷起台灣經濟<br />\n<br />\n喺香港捱層樓，倒不如去台灣做開荒牛"},{"pid":"71f8ced9537bbcb76b8862887aef196662a05a16","tid":1303344,"uid":225977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"唔想去其他國家做蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb9dd8d4a2955b093376ae35f86ceb13752a0b5","tid":1303344,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:47:24.000Z","msg":"班台仔日日中國香港咁叫你估下佢地會唔會同意"},{"pid":"96fcb25b7aac1eacd125b12ea7532d8e895bb44b","tid":1303344,"uid":238628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"到時台灣人眼中既香港人<br />\n會變成依家香港人眼中既大陸人"},{"pid":"c7726e11c82963087d99fffb1eb5ccc0c4be70fc","tid":1303344,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"香港人幫台灣手發展經濟<br />\n有人才吸引外資 又有錢消費<br />\n比個安心地我地移民 交多啲稅又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3ec44dfcb14acbb0e9453aba9a2905058cbe00","tid":1303344,"uid":14328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71f8ced9537bbcb76b8862887aef196662a05a16","tid":1303344,"uid":225977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"唔想去其他國家做蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲並唔係你移民過去就係蝗蟲<br />\n<br />\n而係你個行為本身，要好似大陸人咁，搶人資源，又要串串貢，聲大夾惡<br />\n咁先係蝗蟲。"},{"pid":"80dce8193b93ce90265bf8f9eaf4914a4a4b61e1","tid":1303344,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96fcb25b7aac1eacd125b12ea7532d8e895bb44b","tid":1303344,"uid":238628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"到時台灣人眼中既香港人<br />\n會變成依家香港人眼中既大陸人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"品格好，質素高，唔搶人資源，唔貪威識食，我諗佢地會歡迎掛？<br />\n<br />\n要做到好似日本人／德國人咁，你移民去邊度，人地都歡迎你，而且係想你移過去。"},{"pid":"ae2b2f7cabaee3e4b44a61765cd7dae2c4c8e7eb","tid":1303344,"uid":197149,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"我地唔想多如蝗蟲大陸人嚟香港生活，蠶食文化，<br />\n台灣人亦唔會想非台灣人喺屬於自己嘅地方生活，蠶食佢地嘅文化<br />\n台灣人支持嘅係我地為自由而反抗極權嘅理念，唔代表支持我地喺佢地地方分享本來全屬於佢地嘅資源"},{"pid":"e5c247b465831c2c69eb190be3196b24a1875d61","tid":1303344,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"你估佢地唔驚比中共滲透咩"},{"pid":"1238da870b26ddaa5f3420bd5cc6637eece0b3c3","tid":1303344,"uid":170929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e3ec44dfcb14acbb0e9453aba9a2905058cbe00","tid":1303344,"uid":14328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71f8ced9537bbcb76b8862887aef196662a05a16","tid":1303344,"uid":225977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"唔想去其他國家做蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲並唔係你移民過去就係蝗蟲<br />\n<br />\n而係你個行為本身，要好似大陸人咁，搶人資源，又要串串貢，聲大夾惡<br />\n咁先係蝗蟲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"咪係，有貢獻有付出既就唔係蝗蟲啦，蝗蟲係指果班落黎香港拎綜援又走水貨既大陸人"},{"pid":"c2946ee97b9d9fe036e9d444371eb2e3ca08a6f3","tid":1303344,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71f8ced9537bbcb76b8862887aef196662a05a16","tid":1303344,"uid":225977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"唔想去其他國家做蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"過去有貢獻下社會<br />\n自給自足 唔做大食懶等政府養<br />\n尊重&amp;融入當地文化<br />\n唔係叫人就番你轉頭<br />\n咁就唔係蝗啦"},{"pid":"c70608196c2888cf812855b8a6de5b95f757151c","tid":1303344,"uid":81389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:54:30.000Z","msg":"係既東部我都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8610b4578a6ca8bb1469c213964e0a9906093b2f","tid":1303344,"uid":225977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e3ec44dfcb14acbb0e9453aba9a2905058cbe00","tid":1303344,"uid":14328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71f8ced9537bbcb76b8862887aef196662a05a16","tid":1303344,"uid":225977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"唔想去其他國家做蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲並唔係你移民過去就係蝗蟲<br />\n<br />\n而係你個行為本身，要好似大陸人咁，搶人資源，又要串串貢，聲大夾惡<br />\n咁先係蝗蟲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"移民其他國家一定用人哋唔少資源<br />\n例如醫療、教育之類<br />\n同埋你控制唔到其他人嘅品行"},{"pid":"b38ad1ef6dc80e8994f3c223a9285740075e2769","tid":1303344,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"己所不欲，勿施於人<br />\n你咁樣同蝗蟲有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bb8805d56a97c903175e351f63c89e8c62fa3d","tid":1303344,"uid":82457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"你可以諗<br />\n台灣唔會諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試下咪咁天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140bfa2fdd8a881aaa9edeeca26c871b366eed8b","tid":1303344,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"由一個中國去另一個中國 no la <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實台灣唔難去 想去嘅自己直接移民過去就得"},{"pid":"0428a65cc95500ebd19b76d3c954b9917cd9d663","tid":1303344,"uid":241101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"140bfa2fdd8a881aaa9edeeca26c871b366eed8b","tid":1303344,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"由一個中國去另一個中國 no la <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實台灣唔難去 想去嘅自己直接移民過去就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"大量真。港人一齊過去，有community就唔同講法<br />\n<br />\n移民到歐美，始終唔同膚色就係二等公民<br />\n搵到個同種族、價值文化語言近似嘅地方集體移民係好難得<br />\n<br />\n所以台灣如果真係做，絕對有得諗<br />\n起碼港人可以升格變左有獨立主權嘅國家先<br />\n代價（錢、適應期、被歧視風險）又唔大"},{"pid":"1ac4c166ede701bddc98d54e3a055764d60222b6","tid":1303344,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LksKD1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLksKD1K.png&h=d604dfb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGakcmL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGakcmL.png&h=aca25f88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22a5bb05a588d4578f364bf5f0031a1328a1f94e","tid":1303344,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5c23beda64203faa168d67953d62973ae215cb3","tid":1303344,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:26:40.000Z","msg":"低價低門檻會引左D咩人過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8efbd2b472119a006e72bddfd6dea45a08dd2e","tid":1303344,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"大量香港人去<br />\n會改變台灣人現有生活模式<br />\n人地想唔想先？<br />\n<br />\n如果下一屆由支那囯民黨執政<br />\n咁點？"}]}